Detailed Description

Structure defining the properties of divider. Divider is defined as one input and one output.

Field Documentation

regBitField_t* pmhalClockDivider::pDivCtrlBitField

Register bit-field info. If this filed is invalid, then this is a fixed divider and can be programmed. In this case the value pSupportedDivision[0] gives the fixed division value.

validDivValue_t* pmhalClockDivider::pSupportedDivision

Array of allowed divValues

uint8_t pmhalClockDivider::pSupportedDivisionMax

Size of pSupportedDivision array
